question:
Consider the following code. What will be the output?

```java
interface Formatter {
    static String format(String input) {
        return "Formatted: " + input.toUpperCase();
    }
}

class DataPrinter implements Formatter {
    String printData(String data) {
        return format(data); // Line A
    }
}

public class Test {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        DataPrinter printer = new DataPrinter();
        System.out.println(printer.printData("hello"));
    }
}
```
